file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 20-10-09-04 - TUBING JOINTS - REMOVAL/INSTALLATION

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL TUBING JOINTS - REMOVAL/INSTALLATION EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. The procedures for the typical removal of the pneumatic line joints are given in AMM TASK 36-11-09-000-801-A/400, AMM TASK 36-11-09-000-802-A/400 or AMM TASK 36-11-10-000-801- A/400, as applicable. B. The procedures for the typical installation of the pneumatic line joints are given in AMM TASK 36-11-09-400-801-A/400, AMM TASK 36-11-09-400-802-A/400 or AMM TASK 36-11-10-400-801- A/400, as applicable. C. The procedures for the typical removal of the fuel line joints are given in AMM TASK 28-21-13-000-801-A/400 or AMM TASK 28-21-13-000-802-A/400, as applicable. D. The procedures for the typical installation of the fuel line joints are given in AMM TASK 28-21-13-400-801-A/400 or AMM TASK 28-21-13-400-802-A/400, as applicable.
